		<td><b>Kid Niki 3 ?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Anybody made a MMC-3 mapper hacked version of this game on TSROM board? I tried but it wasnt working. Used this to go by:
<br />TKROM &amp; TSROM (mapper 4): 
<br />PRG socket: Bend up pins 1, 2, 24, 30 and 31 (or cut tracks 2, 24, 30 and 31) 
<br />Solder pin 2 to hole 24 (A16) 
<br />Solder pin 24 to GND (OE) 
<br />Solder pin 30 to hole 1 (A17) 
<br />Solder pin 31 to hole 2 (A18) 
<br />CHR socket: Bend up pins 1, 2, 22, 24, 30, 31 (or cut tracks 2, 22, 24 and 30) 
<br />Solder pin 2 to hole 24 (A16) 
<br />Solder pin 22 to hole 31 (CE or CHR /A13) 
<br />Solder pin 24 to hole 2 (OE or CHR /RD) 
<br />Solder pin 30 to hole 1 (A17)
<br />
<br />Is this right or am i missing something? Im using a waldo cart.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


